Template: iodine/sercives_config_info
Type: note
Description: Extra configuration required for iodine services
  Before you start iodine's client and server services via systemd, please edit the following files to your specific needs:
 .
 /etc/sysconfig/iodine-client: Client configuration.
 /etc/sysconfig/iodine-server: Server configuration.
 .
 For details on how to setup the aforementioned configurations, please see iodine(8).
Description-zh_CN.UTF-8: iodine 服务需要额外设置
 在启动 iodine 客户端或服务端前，您需要预先编辑如下配置文件：
 .
 /etc/sysconfig/iodine-client：客户端配置文件
 /etc/sysconfig/iodine-server：服务端配置文件
 .
 有关上述配置的编写方式，请详见 iodine(7)。
